      "span_text": "Cloning of the Rab5B, Rab6A, and Rab7 proteins from L. vannamei Partial cDNA sequences that are homologous to Drosophila Rab5B, Rab6A, and Rab7 were retrieved from the sequenced L. vannamei transcriptome data, which was previously completed in our research group"
